<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.6.8">
<l>ceḻunīrma larkkamalan tiraiyuntu vaṉpakaṭṭāl</l>
<l>uḻunīrva yaluḻava ruḻappiṉmuṉ piḻaitteḻunta</l>
<l>kaḻunīrka ṭikamaḻuṅ kaṭaṉmallait talacayaṉam</l>
<l>toḻunīrma ṉattavarait tōḻuvāyeṉ tūyneñcē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>My pure heart, worship those whose minds are worshipful in Talacayaṉam</l>
<l>At Mallai by the sea, scented by fragrant waterlilies which rise up,</l>
<l>Dodging back and forth as the ploughmen plough wet fields</l>
<l>Ploughed with strong bulls which push ripples in the fertile waters</l>
<l rend="indent">[full of] lotus blossoms.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
